      <title>巴勒斯坦人废除以色列认为恐怖主义的津贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/palestinians-scrap-stipends-that-israel-saw-as-stoking-terrorism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦总统马哈茂德·阿巴斯（Mahmoud Abbas）说，他正在取消向与以色列战争中被判入狱或杀害的人支付的津贴，因为他的政府试图与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普建立联系，并争夺战后加沙的角色。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/palestinians-scrap-stipends-that-israel-saw-as-stoking-terrorism</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 18:40:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的成本切割者希望遏制德勤，其他FEMA合同</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/fema-contracts-like-deloitte-being-reviewed-by-trump-s-cost-cutters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）推动的联邦削减成本计划将其重点转移到了联邦紧急事务管理局（Federal Emergy Management Agency）上，在那里，在德勤（Deloitte）等顾问的支出现在面临审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/fema-contracts-like-deloitte-being-reviewed-by-trump-s-cost-cutters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 18:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国表示，尽管有报复风险，但仍将保留数字税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/france-says-it-will-keep-digital-tax-despite-retaliation-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长埃里克·伦巴德（Eric Lombard）表示，法国不会放弃其数字税，即在加剧贸易紧张局势加剧的情况下，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）遭受了唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的安抚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/france-says-it-will-keep-digital-tax-despite-retaliation-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 18:21:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈塞特说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/hassett-says-trump-s-treasuries-remark-was-on-payments-not-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周末关于国库付款中违规行为的评论是指亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）的说法，即政府已向承包商和授予接收者及其授予的接收者进行了不当转移。总统的最高经济顾问周一表示，对债券持有人的付款的关注不关心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/hassett-says-trump-s-treasuries-remark-was-on-payments-not-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 18:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国寻求明确的特朗普关税，以避免钢铁威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/uk-seeks-clarity-on-trump-tariffs-in-bid-to-avoid-steel-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士说，英国官员将与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）政府的同行交谈，以避免总统宣布的钢铁和铝的25％关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/uk-seeks-clarity-on-trump-tariffs-in-bid-to-avoid-steel-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:34:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔（Powell</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/powell-heads-for-hyper-charged-hearings-overshadowed-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）本周在国会山（Capitol Hill）面临着一场艰难的听证会，民主党人和共和党人都可能会根据总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的政策，从银行法规到多样性，公平和包容性工作的回滚，这些政策已经吞没了中央中央的努力银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/powell-heads-for-hyper-charged-hearings-overshadowed-by-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普放弃了禁止海外贿赂的美国法律执行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-to-loosen-enforcement-of-us-law-banning-overseas-bribes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统将签署一项行政命令，以退缩一项法律，这使美国公司贿赂外国官员是非法的，认为这一限制使美国公司处于不利地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/trump-to-loosen-enforcement-of-us-law-banning-overseas-bribes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:29:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列，哈马斯交易指控违反停战交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/israel-hamas-exchange-accusations-of-ceasefire-deal-violation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列和哈马斯互相指控违反了上个月同意停火协议的条款，这引起了人们对在最初六周最初的六周中大约一半休战的持久性的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/israel-hamas-exchange-accusations-of-ceasefire-deal-violation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:06:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科索沃的总理面临联盟挑战，以扩大他的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/kosovo-s-premier-faces-coalition-challenge-to-extend-his-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科索沃总理可能在他自己努力遵守民族主义政策和反腐败措施所需的多数之后，可能会努力成立新政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-10/kosovo-s-premier-faces-coalition-challenge-to-extend-his-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 17:03:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划对钢，铝进口征收25％的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-plans-to-announce-25-steel-aluminum-tariffs-on-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统计划对美国所有进口钢铁和铝征收25％的关税，从而扩大了他对该国一些顶级贸易伙伴的贸易限制，并寻求保护去年帮助他赢得战场国家的家庭行业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/trump-plans-to-announce-25-steel-aluminum-tariffs-on-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 21:33:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
